  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hiring a car and hitting the road, is one of the best ways to see Calabria. On this self-drive tour we’ve done all the planning for you so all you need to do is enjoy the experience. On this week long road trip you’ll get to discover <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/calabria" title="Calabria">Calabria's</a> art, history, culture, beautiful coastline and mountainous scenery. Explore this lesser known region at your own pace, as you drive from the beaches of Capo Vaticano to the hilltop villages of the Pollino National park, stopping to see ancient castles and try tasty local foods along the way.</p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/calabria-self-drive#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/calabria-self-drive#Itinerary&quot;">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/calabria-self-drive#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/calabria-self-drive#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/calabria-self-drive#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
