<h2><a name="Hotels"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Hotels</span><span class="geolocation-title"></span></h2>
<p>Please note that these hotels are subject to availability at the time of booking. If these are not available, they will be changed to hotels of a similar standard and location.</p>
<p><strong>★★★ Hotel Cristina, Diamante area (2 nights)</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★ La Magara, Civita area (1 night)</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★ Locandiera, Scilla area (1 night)</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★★ Hotel Cannamele Resort, near Tropea (3 nights)</strong></p>
<p><strong>Your Food: </strong>Breakfast is included at each hotel. If you choose half board you’ll have dinner in the hotel restaurants. If the hotel does not have a dinner service, you’ll dine at a local restaurant.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2><a name="Departure dates"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Departure dates<a></a></span></h2>
<p>Flexible daily departures from May to October</p>
